## Description
PK-55H belongs to the "Противопригарные покрытия" range and is intended to keep foundry operations stable.
- Suitable for processes: Альфа-cет, Фуран, Резол-CO₂, ЖСС, Пеп-сет and Кронинг.
- Base: Спиртовое.

## Application
- Stir the product before use and confirm it matches your application method.
- Run a small-scale trial to set the required consumption rate and drying modes.
- Record the parameters that deliver the desired surface quality and mold stability.

## Good to know
- Follow safety guidance and provide ventilation during preparation and application.
- Monitor viscosity/density regularly and adjust with solvent or additives if the instruction allows.
- Store the product in sealed containers, avoiding moisture and temperature swings.
